# .trivyignore — accept ONLY what cannot be fixed, each with a reason + review date.
# Anything fixable (undici, etc.) is fixed in code/image and does NOT belong here.

# AVD-DS-0026 (LOW): Dockerfile without HEALTHCHECK.
# Reason: the healthcheck is defined at the orchestration layer — docker-compose (app/nginx),
#   and, under Kubernetes, liveness/readiness probes (a Dockerfile HEALTHCHECK is ignored under k8s).
#   Duplicating it in the Dockerfile = redundant.
# Accepted: 2026-06-23. Review: when Kubernetes probes are introduced — confirm they cover this.
AVD-DS-0026

